{"title":"在头里","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在头里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河北兴隆半壁山公社　刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老贫农刘自奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绰号“在头里”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土改斗地主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在最头里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开账本算血泪债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开仓分粮给穷兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成立公社时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在最头里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举大旗，呼口号："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海枯石烂心不移！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种地在头里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是他插下第一犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出工在头里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里含饭就下地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队里公布账目，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他总挨着会计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼盯的准，耳听的真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分分厘厘记心里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女儿上党员训练班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚走一步他催的急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快点去，快点去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听毛主席是咋说的！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿当车把式，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腿迟一步他不依，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“给社办事要加紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刻不能忘社会主义。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看在头里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想在头里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说在头里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干在头里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心怀社会主义事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩扛集体化大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农本色永不变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的好膀臂！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}